                            <Heading/>
                            <Paragraph>The Administration for Children and Families
                                        administers programs and provides advice to the Secretary on
                                        issues relevant to children, youth, and families; child
                                        support enforcement; community services; developmental
                                        disabilities; family assistance; Native American assistance;
