                <Header>Archived Records</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Guide to Federal Records in the National Archives of the United States" indicates that Administration records have been assigned to record group 292. The guide does not contain, however, a description that is associated with this record group. In anticipation of the transfer of archival records, record group 292 was created; however, no transfer had occurred before the guide was last updated.</Paragraph>
